snippet.textDisplay:
I've played this song so many times just because of QB's voice and her style of singing.
But then Umair's part, the overall composition, every musical artist. Everything is just perfect.
And then there's the tragic tale this song tells.
There are so many levels to this song.

Started listening it during my college term and somehow those exact happy feelings come back to me every time I listen to this it.
This song is the definition of bliss.
